Wycliffe Osabwa: With toothless agencies, voter our only hope

In a recent pronouncement, the president of the Law Society of Kenya, Nelson Havi, stated that neither the Ethics and Anti-Corruption Authority (EACC) nor the Independent Electoral and Boundaries Commission (IEBC) has the legal mandate to bar an aspirant from vying for an elective seat.



